Introduction

Chien Tzuling (Korean: 젠쯔링; Chinese: 簡紫翎; Japanese: ジエン·ツーリン) is a Taiwanese singer under EVA Entertainment. She debuted as a member of the girl group ViV on April 11, 2024 with their single album "Bomb".

She is best known for being a contestant on the South Korean reality survival show Girls Planet 999 and participated in the Taiwanese survival show Next Girlz.
